## STEP 2ï¸âƒ£ â€” Draw the FLOW (Boxes + Arrows in Your Head)

Ask only this:

> â€œWhat happens next?â€

```
Start
 â†“
Insert Card
 â†“
Enter PIN
 â†“
Choose Option
 â†“
Do Work
 â†“
