# Minimal ATM Design Using This Method

### 1. User Story

```
Insert card â†’ Enter pin â†’ Choose option â†’ Done
```

### 2. Flow

```
Idle â†’ Authenticated â†’ Transaction â†’ Exit
```

### 3. Split

* Input: menu
* Logic: balance
